data.description: Beautiful home with everything you would expect and more! Walk up to the welcoming front porch and into the foyer with hardwood floors and follow into the fireside family room with soaring ceiling and stack stone fireplace. Kitchen features stained cabinets, huge island, breakfast bar, breakfast nook all with a open view to the family room. Full finished basement with possilbe 5th bedroom, media/game room and second family room and full bath. Oversized master and 3 additional bedrooms upstairs. Community has is all, swim, tennis, trails, basketball, playground.
